'''Père David's snowfinch''' ('''''Pyrgilauda davidiana'''''), also known as the '''small snowfinch''', is a [[species]] of bird in the [[Old World sparrow|sparrow]] family.

It is found in Mongolia, southern [[Siberia]] and northern China. Its natural [[habitat]] is temperate [[grassland]].

